episodes.title: Cult found guilty, Former Bishop of Broom faces new child sexual abuse charges
episodes.description: 14 members of a Queensland religious cult are today confirmed killers found guilty, of the manslaughter of a little girl in a historic verdict. The former Bishop of Broom is facing a string of new child sexual abuse charges. 7NEWS Headlines with Edwina Bartholomew for January 30, 2025.
